{"tid":2342234,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"再講一次黃店無心做不如直接搞眾籌算","createTime":"2020-12-27T03:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T11:00:55.000Z","uid":115660,"like":114,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"00b840b4ed10cf59d9152a1a2669ba6bd63f2724","tid":2342234,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"搞乜撚飲食<br />\n野又細細碟<br />\n又貴<br />\n跟住話要養手足<br />\n<br />\n搞乜撚野飲食姐<br />\n直接搞個眾籌基金叫人捐錢咪算<br />\n<br />\n捐完錢送盒雞翼我食我都無咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n但搞清楚你依家係搞飲食 唔係乞 唔係搞眾籌<br />\n<br />\n你有責任去maintain 食物既 水準 份量 質素<br />\n<br />\n唔好乜都用黃店做擋箭牌"},{"pid":"20d7f6e527522529c374cae5ea32bd9ec483cb2d","tid":2342234,"uid":115660,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"7de1d5b9d69ffe6868e7c17868925cf97a6a56a2","tid":2342234,"uid":62259,"like":20,"dislike":17,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"根據連登仔標準<br />\n你屌黃店姐係五毛分化撚<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"61d37cbe49f23e2c3a0f1bd6a88c9157b7878c8b","tid":2342234,"uid":115660,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7de1d5b9d69ffe6868e7c17868925cf97a6a56a2","tid":2342234,"uid":62259,"like":20,"dislike":17,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"根據連登仔標準<br />\n你屌黃店姐係五毛分化撚<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"咁我邊一句有講錯"},{"pid":"6bc5ae57ff354e66265ddb193897ab26c50ede60","tid":2342234,"uid":262674,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"如果真係做唔到質素<br />\n可以唔做食肆<br />\n<br />\n賣下凍肉生果容易啲"},{"pid":"d2c40c27646b916ec33c90888a703cf7bbe03b6d","tid":2342234,"uid":62259,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d37cbe49f23e2c3a0f1bd6a88c9157b7878c8b","tid":2342234,"uid":115660,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7de1d5b9d69ffe6868e7c17868925cf97a6a56a2","tid":2342234,"uid":62259,"like":20,"dislike":17,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"根據連登仔標準<br />\n