食是良知</strong></span></span><br />\n仲要份量咁樣嚟呃人<br />\n基本野都做唔到學咩人開店<br />\n幾黃都無用囉 又用黃嚟做擋箭牌</blockquote><br />\n真呀 黃店大曬<br />\n<br />\n我遲d拎自己d底褲去賣<br />\n叫人撐手足"},{"pid":"c441e458cb614a05af3c1585a8159ae4d919a3a4","tid":2342234,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"唔認同，我覺得一定要支持黃圈，不過我窮撚無辦法，只可以食住啲平價大集團藍店先，等黃店俾其他手足養肥左出到同大集團一樣既平價野又多分店既時候我一定會幫襯返黃店，支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以麻煩大家食多啲黃店等佢可以快啲同大集團撼，咁我就可以快啲有得食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f43352d106056dd4e3349daa18a58cfc4206f6","tid":2342234,"uid":196221,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講句 大部分黃店只不過係運動前難食到準備執笠既鋪頭 我去十間食 有九間都係又貴又難食"},{"pid":"ef40dad1639d3ab644f11d2e8eb0e8d5c11068f8","tid":2342234,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"俾多啲意粉飯幾多錢姐<br />\n根本就冇心做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2796cb6539d6a113e2ca0d9283994668a50254f0","tid":2342234,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7de1d5b9d69ffe6868e7c17868925cf97a6a56a2","tid":2342234,"uid":62259,"like":20,"dislike":17,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"根據連登仔標準<br />\n你屌黃店姐係五毛分化撚<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"漏咗pr"},{"pid":"e620718f027637e4ba6b17d13555c4c01c84506f","tid":2342234,"uid":74058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"881415e310d2075d723689c6e1e995ea952edb34","tid":2342234,"uid":59297,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">起底自己諗</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lgm1f3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgm1f3f.png&h=b237de3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3aEM9W.png\" data-thumbnail-sr